comments: She is a great English teacher. She is very clear about her expectations and lays out how to pass her class and if you do those things, you will pass well. She is not at all a tough grader and only assigns 4 essays for the entire semester. It is discussion based and hw is key but you have a week to do it. Not an easy A but not too hard either.

comments: I can honestly say that I LOVED this class. I had her on tuesdays from 6:20-10:00pm. She NEVER kept us the entire time (which was great), and her class was the best class I had all semester. She expects you to be on time with the book in hand. You have 1 paper due every 2-3 weeks and she is very clear in her requirements. Read, share, and show up!
